  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This basic Kendo-style attack targets the side torso area in an attempt to rupture or nauseate the foe.<br><br>The user must be wielding a Kendo Stick in order to perform this technique. The user makes an attack roll at a -2 penalty specifically targeting the torso area. This attack deals normal weapon damage and causes the target to become nauseated for 1 round unless he succeeds a Fortitude save.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Material Focus:</b> The user's held Kendo Stick.</p>\n<p><b>Mastery:</b> Each mastery in this technique increases the save DC by 1.</p>\n",
